  "instructions": [
    "Heat melted butter in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and sauté until translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add chopped gomen and cook until wilted, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add king prawns and cook until pink and fully cooked, about 2-3 minutes per side.",
    "Stir in bergamot juice and Ethiopian red pepper powder.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional gomen if desired."
